Re: どそりゃ
by Hyperworm » Mon 09.05.2011 7:58 am Parsing error! (So often this is the problem...)だけど(however) + そりゃ（＝それは）だけど is だ(＝です) + けど. See also だが. Basically means the same thing as しかし. fun translation snippets | need something translated?BTC@1KMZXgoWiDshQis5Z7feCx8jaiP4QAB2ks
Hyperworm
Posts: 493Joined: Tue 11.20.2007 2:26 pm
