Re: どそりゃ
by micahcowan » Tue 09.06.2011 2:10 pm So, given what Hyperworm has pointed out, a better translation (without knowing anything further about the context) might be, "But that's a mistake." だけど but; そりゃ that; 間違い a mistake; だ is/(copula). Other translations are possible, but "You were only wrong" is not one of the possibilities.
Micah J Cowan
http://www.JapaneseReader.com
